name: Chest Press Machine
details: The chest press machine is an excellent exercise for beginners. It provides an effective but straightforward way to work your upper body.

name: Hammer Strength Machine
details: Hammer Strength machines provide a great workout for all of your muscles, helping to improve their tone and appearance.

name: Pec Fly Machine
details: The chest fly machine is often overlooked in the weight room because there are so many different ways to work the chest (pectoralis) muscles.

name: abdominal roller
details: The ab roller is an excellent exercise for working the upper body musculature too, including the erector spinae, the stabilizing muscles running the length of your spine

name: weightlifting
details: Strength training can help you manage or lose weight, and it can increase your metabolism to help you burn more calories.
